  "design_notes": "Hard chart with a steady build-up and physical drop. Intro uses simple taps to warm up. Build part 1 features light zigzagging streams. Build part 2 introduces running man steps moving left to right. Climax of build ups intensity with crossovers and quick accents. First half of drop uses heavy jumpstream with moderate crossovers. Second drop half peaks with box patterns and complex holds. Syncopation section has quick drills to match peak vocals. Outro serves as a comfortable stops-breather to conclude the experience.",
